lead_paragraph: Harrison Barnes and Andrew Bogut are in, Chandler Parsons and Zaza Pachulia are out and Dallas coach Rick Carlisle has a retooled roster for the sixth consecutive time since winning a championship.

headline.print_headline: Barnes, Bogut Highlight Latest Round of Changes for Mavs
